every night there's a gala.

00:27:36.082 --> 00:27:38.540
Sometimes there's more than
one gala, and you're competing.

00:27:38.540 --> 00:27:39.380
And who's made what?

00:27:39.380 --> 00:27:41.714
And people are there with all
their money and flashiness

00:27:41.714 --> 00:27:42.671
and all the rest of it.

00:27:42.671 --> 00:27:44.495
But one of the things
that we wanted to do,

00:27:44.495 --> 00:27:46.620
and one of my missions
certainly, with Make-A-Wish,

00:27:46.620 --> 00:27:50.490
and I know that Make-A-Wish
follows me with this too,

00:27:50.490 --> 00:27:53.540
is that it isn't just about
a few wealthy people getting

00:27:53.540 --> 00:27:55.850
involved, that Make-A-Wish
has always been inclusive.

00:27:55.850 --> 00:27:59.520
And to open the gala
and stream it live

00:27:59.520 --> 00:28:03.040
and to invite the public,
really, into the gala,

00:28:03.040 --> 00:28:05.680
to be able to be a part of it,
was important for Make-A-Wish

00:28:05.680 --> 00:28:07.630
and myself.

00:28:07.630 --> 00:28:09.870
And it was the first time
they'd ever done that.

00:28:09.870 --> 00:28:13.210
And I feel that going
forward, the gala itself

00:28:13.210 --> 00:28:17.910
will evolve into a far more
inclusive and involved event.

00:28:17.910 --> 00:28:19.830
That really the
Gala ends up being

00:28:19.830 --> 00:28:22.640
a kickoff for a larger
campaign that people

00:28:22.640 --> 00:28:23.830
can be more involved with.

00:28:23.830 --> 00:28:26.550
Versus sort of one night
of fund raising, it

00:28:26.550 --> 00:28:28.080
needs to be an ongoing event.

00:28:28.080 --> 00:28:31.630
And as we've said multiple
times, it takes an army.

00:28:31.630 --> 00:28:33.240
It takes a village.

00:28:33.240 --> 00:28:37.820
All these wishes are
created by everybody

00:28:37.820 --> 00:28:39.830
getting involved and
playing their part,

00:28:39.830 --> 00:28:42.450
from feeding people to
driving people over,

00:28:42.450 --> 00:28:44.660
to all the little aspects.

00:28:44.660 --> 00:28:46.250
Maybe you're donating
your air miles,

00:28:46.250 --> 00:28:48.510
or you yourself are
donating your time.

00:28:48.510 --> 00:28:51.360
Time is the one
thing that we need.

00:28:51.360 --> 00:28:52.450
It isn't the money.

00:28:52.450 --> 00:28:53.550
The money is fantastic.

00:28:53.550 --> 00:28:55.630
