any of us ever really want,

00:29:08.150 --> 00:29:11.830
is someone to listen
and to care and to stop

00:29:11.830 --> 00:29:15.830
for a second in that busy life
that they lead and to focus.

00:29:15.830 --> 00:29:17.660
And I think that
focus is something

00:29:17.660 --> 00:29:22.956
which we can't put a dollar
value on, but it's invaluable.

00:29:22.956 --> 00:29:25.330
And that's something which we
